** a non technical team member  comes to you and says "the site is slow"
Have the candidate walk through how the would trouble shoot the question

See if they first question the human aspect of the scenario. What's slow

Guide them through each layer of the stack if they skip over frontend or backend
redirect them and say "what if the problem is narrowed down to a backend issue"

look for how to debug sql with Describe and indexing

look for caching ideas and infrastructure

